output.sentences: A lonely little car was thinking about joining a race.
He joined 4 other cars at the starting line, ready to roll.
The little black car won their race by a mile.
Then, he posed at the finish line with his driver and owners.
The lonely little car was inspired by the black car's victory to keep racing and win his own trophy someday.
